  • com.veepoo.protocol.VPOperateManager

  • public class VPOperateManager

    • 【Focus】The main class that needs to be operated The device does not support asynchronous operations. When multiple time-consuming operations are performed simultaneously, data may be confusing. Therefore, had better not do multiple operations at the same time SDK Version:2.1.65.15
    • 【重点关注】主要操作类,也是唯一需要操作的类 设备不支持异步操作,当多个耗时操作同时进行时,可能会导致数据紊乱; 因此在与设备进行交互时,尽可能避免多个操作同时进行 SDK Version:2.1.75.15

  • startDetectBP

    public void startDetectBP(IBleWriteResponse bleWriteResponse,
                          IBPDetectDataListener bpDetectDataListener,
                          EBPDetectModel model)

    • Start detect the blood pressure in real-time when you start detect the blood pressure, you need to create the object to save the detect status,and you should set the object value to true then,after you get the detect progress value over than or equal 100,you need call the stopDetectBp function immediately ,and set the object value to false the result of detect blood is when progress value is 100

    • 开始手动测量血压 在测量血压的界面下,需要定义一个标志位来表示测量状态,当开始测量时,将状态位置为true, 当获取到测量血压的进度大于等于100时,需要立即调用stopDetectBp,并修改标志位状态为false。 血压的有效值取第一个返回进度为100的血压值。

    参数:
    bleWriteResponse -
    • the response of write oprate,if reponse code equals Code.REQUEST_SUCCESS means write cmd success,otherwise means write cmd fail
    • 写入操作的监听
    bpDetectDataListener -
    • the listener of detect blood pressure
    • 血压数据返回的监听
    model -
    • the detect model;the one thing you should pay attention, if you want detect blood pressure using the private model, you should call the settingDetectBP function to set the low pressure value and high pressure value before. otherwise you would not get the detect result
    • 测试血压的模式,要注意的是使用[私人模式]时确保用户在之前有设置过私人模式下的高低压数据,否则有可能测量不出的数据

    * 假如手表存储的数据是3天 读取所有的健康数据,读取的顺序为 [睡眠数据（今天-昨天-前天）]-[5分钟原始数据(今天-昨天-前天)],便针对原始数据可以进行自定义天的位置,以及条数的位置 ,比如传入[昨天,150],那么读取顺序为 [睡眠数据（今天-昨天-前天）]-[5分钟原始数据(昨天（150）-前天)]
